body:
@girving @sherrym 

I've uninstalled tensorflow and build it from nightly binaries, it is now `0.11.0` version, but still doesn't contain other examples except for mnist tutorials. 

```
/tensorflow
    /examples
        /__pycache__
        /tutortials
            /mnist
                /input_data.py
                /mnist.py
                /__init__.py
                /__pycache__
            /__pycache__
            /__init__.py
        /__init__.py
```
